  <h2>Underwatering</h2>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-9">
      <p>When a succulent is underwatered, the plant's leaves will shrivel up and feel "empty".
      To solve this issue, just water your succulent in the correct increments. Maybe you can set a timer on
      your phone to remind yourself to water the succulent! Be thankful that this is your only problem. Overwatering a succulent
      is much worse!</p>
    </div>
